{"tid":481124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟去剪頭髮俾唔俾貼士好？","createTime":"2017-11-27T00:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T01:45:21.000Z","uid":151877,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f863c2ee06ba78163580e6c4086613def48152e","tid":481124,"uid":151877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T00:34:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟就幫襯開一間沙龍年幾兩年啦<br />\n價錢算中等 150蚊上下<br />\n咁都係因為個髮型師剪嘅啱我心水先繼續剪<br />\n雖然都會有失手嘅時候 不過大部分都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔似某d髮型師咁好似聽唔明中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真啦 一個人同你剪頭髮 佢有無用心去做呢件事<br />\n你係會feel到嘅 我感覺佢每次都好俾心機去剪<br />\n所以我每次走果陣都會俾20蚊落佢手度當鼓勵<br />\n<br />\n利申 做過服務業 明白一日企咁多個鐘好辛苦<br />\n         有人俾貼士真係好開心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />      俾少少當鼓勵 對大家都有好處<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    俾咩啊 埋單份錢包埋架 你估60蚊QB啊"},{"pid":"0d2d64fcf6ebc1f3db5c29341e0a8c47ad474746","tid":481124,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T00:36:54.000Z","msg":"剪得好會比 剪得唔好唔會"},{"pid":"0aab54389e976dff2e7f00c46a6686b2cc8f4560","tid":481124,"uid":151877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T00:54:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32af39dee903538803c0a761c1af6559dd12da08","tid":481124,"uid":151877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T00:54:54.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"308592f7c999d30a6541c2b7522c7285e5868dfd","tid":481124,"uid":125432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T00:59:12.000Z","msg":"有多餘錢咪比、無咪唔比<br />\n如果剪個頭剪得好唔好、係同比幾多貼士有關<br />\n建議你轉過第二間好過"},{"pid":"b8e4912172b5eec18c2e0f33bfa7efb76a505f1c","tid":481124,"uid":151877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:02:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有多餘錢咪比、無咪唔比<br />\n如果剪個頭剪得好唔好、係同比幾多貼士有關<br />\n建議你轉過第二間好過</blockquote><br />\n所以一直轉  直到遇到呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0616ac57bd6e2015c2de37ed90302388c4829bc7","tid":481124,"uid":41569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:24:55.000Z","msg":"覺得掂既又俾得開心既咪俾囉<br />\n我通常洗頭師傅各50"},{"pid":"a40915a19088b395dc8f5697eece99227422aa01","tid":481124,"uid":151877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:44:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺得掂既又俾得開心既咪俾囉<br />\n我通常洗頭師傅各50</blockquote><br />\n洗頭 同 師傅 各50 咁未100"},{"pid":"2cd092da208bf50dbc262febef091e7b8422d7c7","tid":481124,"uid":151877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺得掂既又俾得開心既咪俾囉<br />\n我通常洗頭師傅各50</blockquote><br />\n洗頭 同 師傅 各50 咁未100</blockquote><br />\n但係我果間d洗頭妹洗得好hea"}]}